c: 37
v: 102
t: "Manjalo kwathi lapho (indodana yakhe) seyikhule ngokwanele ukuhamba naye wathi, “Oh ndodana yami! Ngempela mina ngibone ephusheni lami\tngikunikela, ngakho-ke bheka ubonani, yathi (indodana yakhe) Oh baba wami! Yenza lokho okuphoqwayo, uzongithola ngingowababekezelayo uma uMvelinqangi ethanda"